According to Ghanasoccernet.com, Amakhosi head coach Steve Komphela is eager to reunite with the 29-year-old defender at Naturena.Komphela and Awal spent time working with Komphela during their time together at Maritzburg United before the defender left the Team of Choice in 2015.Chiefs are on the lookout for new players after releasing seven players following a poor season that saw Amakhosi finishing another season without winning a single trophy.